Cmd
{
    Does basic checkings
    Loads preference files (if any)
    Loads and creates internal state (if any)
    Manages shell activities
}
    InternalState
    {
    	Singleton class
    	Manager internal properties
    	Can be saved in a file as serialized data
    }
	Shell
	{
	    Interprets commands
	    Calls other commands and supplies with arguments
	    Takes output and displays in console
	    Receives commands from user
	}
		Utilities...
		{
		    Other utilty commands
		}

		
Persistent Storage Files: (all optional)
	Preferences (format: text)
	InternalState (format: binary (serialized data))